  <div class="wrapper">
    <h1>A note from Laurentino</h1>
    <div class="note">
      <div class="note-content">
      <p>Hi there, I'm Laurentino, the creator of Zeuz Visuals.</p>
      <p>Throughout my career, I've helped emerging companies clarify their product vision and often filled the designer role. Other times, I work with founders on product strategy and help them find the perfect full-time designer for their needs. I've also worked with publicly traded companies to unlock their creativity, think about problems differently, and find innovative solutions.</p>
      <p>Whether you're a founder looking for a partner in design and product strategy or an established company working on new features, Iterate can help. I build a custom team around each project I take on and would be excited to work with you.</p>
